			<h2 class="date-header"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-2">06 February 2008</kw></h2>
	
	<div class="entry" id="entry-45201280">
					<h3 class="entry-header"><a href="http://danielhernandez.typepad.com/daniel_hernandez/2008/02/scenes-from-a-m.html"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-2">Scenes from a manga comic convention in Mexico City</kw></a></h3>
		
		<div class="entry-content">
			<div class="entry-body">
				<p><a href="http://danielhernandez.typepad.com/.shared/image.html?/photos/uncategorized/2008/02/05/dsc01820.jpg" onclick="window.open(this.href, '_blank', 'width=800,height=600,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0'); return false"><img alt="Dsc01820" title="Dsc01820" src="http://danielhernandez.typepad.com/daniel_hernandez/images/2008/02/05/dsc01820.jpg" style="width: 455px; height: 340px;" border="0"></a></p>

<p><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">These are just a few of many shots I took at the </kw><a href="http://www.expo-tnt.com/"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">Expo Manga Comic TNT</kw></a><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3"> over the weekend at the </kw><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Trade_Center_M%C3%A9xico"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">World Trade Center</kw></a><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">. It was a huge, three-day comic con even a </kw><a href="http://www.comic-con.org/cci/"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">San Diegan could love</kw></a><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">, with blaring video game consoles, archery, sword jousting, live bands, and </kw><em><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">lots and lots</kw></em><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3"> of people in highly detailed costumes.</kw></p>

<p><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">Trust me, based on interviews and observation, kids in D.F. know their </kw><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Manga"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">manga</kw></a><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">. And Marvel characters. And Harry Potter. And ninja gear. And home-made magical cyborg samurai mouse creatures like homie does below. (He said he got help for his razor-sharp cosmetic dentures from his dad, who is a dentist.)</kw></p>

<p><a onclick="window.open(this.href, '_blank', 'width=800,height=600,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0'); return false" href="http://danielhernandez.typepad.com/.shared/image.html?/photos/uncategorized/2008/02/05/dsc01823.jpg"><img src="http://danielhernandez.typepad.com/daniel_hernandez/images/2008/02/05/dsc01823.jpg" title="Dsc01823" alt="Dsc01823" style="width: 455px; height: 341px;" border="0"></a></p>

<p><a onclick="window.open(this.href, '_blank', 'width=800,height=600,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0'); return false" href="http://danielhernandez.typepad.com/.shared/image.html?/photos/uncategorized/2008/02/05/dsc01808.jpg"><img src="http://danielhernandez.typepad.com/daniel_hernandez/images/2008/02/05/dsc01808.jpg" title="Dsc01808" alt="Dsc01808" style="width: 454px; height: 345px;" border="0"></a></p>

<p><a onclick="window.open(this.href, '_blank', 'width=800,height=600,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0'); return false" href="http://danielhernandez.typepad.com/.shared/image.html?/photos/uncategorized/2008/02/05/dsc01822.jpg"><img src="http://danielhernandez.typepad.com/daniel_hernandez/images/2008/02/05/dsc01822.jpg" title="Dsc01822" alt="Dsc01822" style="width: 454px; height: 341px;" border="0"></a></p>



<p><a href="http://danielhernandez.typepad.com/.shared/image.html?/photos/uncategorized/2008/02/05/dsc01816.jpg" onclick="window.open(this.href, '_blank', 'width=800,height=600,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0'); return false"><img alt="Dsc01816" title="Dsc01816" src="http://danielhernandez.typepad.com/daniel_hernandez/images/2008/02/05/dsc01816.jpg" style="width: 455px; height: 342px;" border="0"></a>


<br><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">* More later ...</kw></p>



