			<h2 class="date-header"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-2">25 June 2007</kw></h2>
	
	<div class="entry" id="entry-35767810">
					<h3 class="entry-header"><a href="http://danielhernandez.typepad.com/daniel_hernandez/2007/06/bleak-blog-week.html"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-2">Bleak blog week, transitions, a new digest</kw></a></h3>
		
		<div class="entry-content">
			<div class="entry-body">
				<p><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">I'll continue with light blogging through this week, due to connection problems at home and a couple project deadlines coming up soon. Meantime, in a new exercise, here's a sampling of links I've been reading today or in the past few days that would otherwise receive more thoughtful treatment:</kw></p><blockquote><p><a href="http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/washingtondc/la-na-poll13jun13,1,7103548.story"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">Large majority supports path to citizenship</kw></a><br><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/24/fashion/24mexican.html?pagewanted=2&amp;_r=2&amp;ref=fashion"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">The Mexican will see you now</kw></a><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3"> (yet another repeat of </kw><a href="http://lists.acomp.usf.edu/pipermail/lls/2006-February/000029.html"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">this original</kw></a><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">)</kw><br><a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/6224054.stm"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">Venezuelan TV may air from Mexico</kw></a><br><a href="http://news.newamericamedia.org/news/view_article.html?article_id=9c223bd0493c9523bff9164e28f329cd"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">More walls won't work in my neighborhood</kw></a><br><a href="http://www.laopinion.com/ciudad/?rkey=00000000000001864530"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">Cedillo proposes teaching of 1929 expulsion of Mexicans</kw></a><br><a href="http://travel.nytimes.com/2007/06/15/us/15taco.html"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">Proposed ban on taco trucks stirs animosity in Salinas</kw></a><br><a href="http://news.newamericamedia.org/news/view_article.html?article_id=4c94d0cfd0bd49faa4ffc2af35689844"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">To get ahead in America, aprenda espaol</kw></a><a href="http://environment.guardian.co.uk/climatechange/story/0,,2111006,00.html?gusrc=rss&amp;feed=networkfront"><br><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">Asian nations accuse West of 'green imperialism'</kw></a><br><a href="http://www.laopinion.com/ciudad/?rkey=00000000000001864240"><kw 